---
// Piano Boss Game
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Piano Boss - The Game</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { background: #1a0a2e; margin: 0; overflow: hidden; border: none; outline: none; }
    canvas { display: block; image-rendering: pixelated; cursor: crosshair; position: fixed; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
    #ui-overlay {
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
    }
    #ui-overlay[hidden] { display: none; }
    #pause-overlay {
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
      z-index: 200;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.75);
    }
    #pause-overlay[hidden] { display: none; }
    .panel { color: #f9fafb;
    .tabs { display: flex; gap: 0; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 14px; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; border: 1.5px solid #4b2d8a; }
    .tab-btn { flex: 1; padding: 10px 0; background: #1a0a2e; border: none; color: #a78bfa; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; border-right: 1px solid #4b2d8a; }
    .tab-btn:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .tab-btn.active { background: #7c3aed; color: #fff; }
    .tab-btn:hover:not(.active) { background: #2d1b69; }
    .tab-content { display: none; width: 100%; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .tab-content.active { display: flex; }
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
      border: 2px solid #7c3aed;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 28px 36px;
      min-width: 320px;
      max-width: 820px;
      width: 92vw;
      max-height: 92vh;
      overflow-y: auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    h2 { color: #fbbf24; font-family: monospace; font-size: 26px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .subtitle { color: #a78bfa; font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-align: center; }
    .coins { color: #22c55e; font-family: monospace; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    button.mbtn {
      width: 260px; padding: 12px 0;
      background: #2d1b69; border: 2px solid #a78bfa; border-radius: 4px;
      color: #f9fafb; font-family: monospace; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    button.mbtn:hover { background: #7c3aed; border-color: #fbbf24; }
    button.mbtn.back { background: #1e1b4b; border-color: #6b7280; margin-top: 14px; }
    button.mbtn.back:hover { background: #374151; }
    .upg-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; width: 100%; }
    .upg-col-hdr { color: #a78bfa; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .upg-card { background: #0f0a2e; border: 1.5px solid #374151; border-radius: 4px; padding: 9px 11px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; }
    .upg-card.can { border-color: #7c3aed; }
    .upg-card.maxed { border-color: #22c55e; }
    .upg-name { color: #f9fafb; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; }
    .upg-desc { color: #9ca3af; font-family: monospace; font-size: 11px; }
    .upg-dots { display: flex; gap: 3px; margin-top: 2px; }
    .upg-dot { width: 10px; height: 8px; background: #374151; border-radius: 1px; }
    .upg-dot.on { background: #22c55e; }
    button.buy-btn { margin-top: 5px; padding: 5px 0; background: #1e1b4b; border: 1.5px solid #fbbf24; border-radius: 3px; color: #fbbf24; font-family: monospace; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; }
    button.buy-btn:hover { background: #7c3aed; }
    button.buy-btn:disabled { border-color: #4b5563; color: #6b7280; background: #111827; cursor: not-allowed; }
    .upg-max { color: #22c55e; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-top: 5px; }
    .txt { color: #e2e8f0; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; }
    .tabs { display: flex; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 12px; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; border: 1.5px solid #4b2d8a; }
    .tab-btn { flex: 1; padding: 10px 0; background: #1a0a2e; border: none; color: #a78bfa; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; border-right: 1px solid #4b2d8a; }
    .tab-btn:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .tab-btn.active { background: #7c3aed; color: #fff; }
    .tab-btn:hover:not(.active) { background: #2d1b69; }
    .tab-pane { display: none; width: 100%; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .tab-pane.active { display: flex; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<canvas id="gameCanvas"></canvas>

<div id="ui-overlay">
  <div id="scr-main" class="panel" style="display:flex">
    <h2>PIANO BOSS</h2>
    <div class="subtitle">Collect notes. Forge chords. Fight music.</div>
    <button class="mbtn" onclick="uiPlay()">PLAY</button>
    <button class="mbtn" onclick="uiUpgrades()">UPGRADES</button>
    <button class="mbtn" onclick="uiShow('scr-levelplan')">LEVEL PLAN</button>
    <button class="mbtn" onclick="uiShow('scr-howtoplay')">HOW TO PLAY</button>
  </div>
  <div id="scr-upgrades" class="panel" style="display:none; max-width:560px">
    <h2>UPGRADES</h2>
    <div class="coins" id="coins-display">Banked: 0</div>
    <div class="tabs">
      <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="uiTab('gun',this)">🔫 Gun</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="uiTab('ability',this)">✨ Ability</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="uiTab('stats',this)">❤️ Base Stats</button>
    </div>
    <div id="tab-gun" class="tab-pane active"></div>
    <div id="tab-ability" class="tab-pane"></div>
    <div id="tab-stats" class="tab-pane"></div>
    <button class="mbtn back" onclick="uiShow('scr-main')">BACK</button>
  </div>
  <div id="scr-levelplan" class="panel" style="display:none">
    <h2>LEVEL PLAN</h2>
    <div class="txt">Stage 1:  Grass Plains       - Bass Brute
Stage 2:  Desert Dunes       - Trumpet Tyrant
Stage 3:  Frozen Tundra      - Drum Destroyer
Stage 4:  Beach              - Violin Viper
Stage 5:  Night Forest       - Sax Specter
Stage 6:  Volcano            - Keyboard Killer
Stage 7:  City Ruins         - Guitar Golem
Stage 8:  Underworld         - Flute Phantom
Stage 9:  Sky Kingdom        - Harp Hunter
Stage 10: Music Meisters Lair - Music Meiser</div>
    <button class="mbtn back" onclick="uiShow('scr-main')">BACK</button>
  </div>
  <div id="scr-howtoplay" class="panel" style="display:none">
    <h2>HOW TO PLAY</h2>
    <div class="txt">WASD - Move     Left Click - Shoot (hold to fire)
Right Click - Forge chord from notes    ESC - Pause

Collect notes on the map (max 12, one per pitch).
Right-click to forge the best chord for coins.
Wrong combo = ALL notes lost!

2 notes: Major3rd/5th=Pistol  Minor3rd=Force  Tritone=Lightning
3 notes: Major=Rifle  Minor=Shotgun  Dim=Grenade
4 notes: Dom7th = Machine Gun

Hit the glowing SAVE flag to bank coins for upgrades.</div>
    <button class="mbtn back" onclick="uiShow('scr-main')">BACK</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="levelup-overlay" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.82);z-index:200;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column">
  <div class="panel" style="min-width:320px;max-width:440px;gap:8px">
    <h2 id="levelup-title" style="color:#fbbf24;margin-bottom:8px">⭐ Level Up!</h2>
    <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:13px;margin:0 0 10px">Choose one free upgrade:</p>
    <div id="levelup-options"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="pause-overlay" style="display:none">
  <div class="panel" style="min-width:260px; gap:12px">
    <h2>PAUSED</h2>
    <button class="mbtn" onclick="uiResume()">RESUME</button>
    <button class="mbtn back" onclick="uiQuit()">QUIT TO MENU</button>
  </div>
</div>

<script is:inline src="/game.js?v=1772423634"></script>
</body>
</html>
